[SkillPath "bidding_conventions/jacoby_2nt_splinters"]
[Student "S"]
{Opening hand with 4-card trump support. You bid 2NT. Partner rebids 3\D.  

The news that partner has a singleton \D does <b>NOT</b> excite you. In fact it causes your hand to devalue a lot. So you use the Principle of Fast Arrival and bid 4\H.}

